name: No Name
description:
I named this piece "No Name" because I'm not sure what I should call it, and I would like some feedback from the viewers!

To send me your suggestions go to: 
http://roygbiv.bigcartel.com/contact

This body of work is 16 x 19, and the medium is acrylic paint

I will be selling this as a limited edition print; signed and numbered!

name: Muscadine Delight
description:
Muscadine Delight was originally a still life. The exaggerated colors, and jagged brush strokes caused the piece to become abstract.

This body of work is 22 x 30, and the medium is acrylic paint.

I will be selling this as an open edition print; signed and numbered!

name: Look In The Mirror
description:
Look In The Mirror is a portrait. Everyone sees themselves differently from how other people view them. 

This person saw untamed and colorful; and most importantly, confident. What do you see yourself as? 

This body of work is 14 x 18, and the medium is prismacolor colored pencil. 

I will be selling this as a limited edition print; signed and numbered!

name: They're Not Ray Bans
description:
They're Not Ray Bans is a portrait bursting with style and pop culture. 

The name simply means that someone can be in touch with today's fashion without worrying about name brands and the price tag that comes on them. 

This body of work is 16 x 18.5, and the medium is acrylic paint. 

I will be selling this as a limited edition print; signed and numbered!

name: Blue Ring
description:
Blue Ring is a portrait representing identity and confidence. 

This piece won a silver medal at Carnegie Hall in New York City. 

The body of work is 18 x 24, and the medium is prismacolor colored pencil.

I will be selling this as a limited edition print; signed and numbered!
